==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛvə(r)|-ɛvə(r)]]

===Adverb===
'''whenever'''

#At [[whatever]] time.
#:''Visit whenever you want to.''
# (''US, colloquial'') When.
#: ''Whenever you get into town, come by and see me.''
# Every time
#: ''Whenever he has a pair of aces, his eyelids twitch.''

